name: Copacabana.
description:
The fishermen colony that has become the main business and service hub, gastronomy, hotels and beaches in Rio de Janeiro!

One of the most beautiful area in Rio De Janeiro, Copacabana is one of the most famous neighborhoods in the city, with tradition and beauty, everything you need for a day at the beach, let's go?
